---
title: Montreal-Spiced Bacon-Wrapped Steak and Shrimp with Garlic Beans, and Creamy Mash
description: Bacon-wrapped steak, need I say more? This pan-seared steak gets the royal treatment with salty, crispy bacon and a rich pan sauce. Flavourful shrimp, creamy mash and garlicky green beans round out this winning weeknight dish.
